title: Giants-Eagles MNF Preview (Eli Returns!), The Ryan Tannehill Takeover (Football 12/9)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Jared Dubin to preview Giants vs Eagles on Monday Night Football (2:00). The guys discuss Eli Manning's return, why Saquon Barkley has been ineffective this season and Carson Wentz's shaky season before issuing player props and picking the game. Then, Jason La Canfora joins the podcast (30:00) to breakdown the Ravens win over the Bills (32:45), another unconvincing victory from Aaron Rodgers and the Packers (36:15), Ryan Tannehill's career resurgence (39:30), David Tepper's vision for the Panthers (49:15), potential changes coming for the Redskins (55:00) and...that Peloton ad (1:05:45).
